OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FA few
OL,6,Fshowers this evening. Then the rest of
OL,7,Fthe night will be mainly dry with
OL,8,Fclear periods and just the odd shower.
OL,9,FCold with patchy frost.
OL,10,
OL,11,CThursday:FMost of the day will be dry,
OL,12,Fsome early brightness. Outbreaks of
OL,13,Frain spreading east towards evening.
OL,14,FColder than of late.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
