OL,5,COutlook for Friday to Sunday:FOvernight
OL,6,Frain clearing on Friday then mainly
OL,7,Fdry, showery rain possible later.
OL,8,FSpells of rain spreading northeast on
OL,9,FSaturday. Cold and bright with
OL,10,Fblustery showers on Sunday. Severe
OL,11,Fgales possible.
